Basra / 1 / 19 Sep 2007 / 0 / 1
Total confirmed cases: 1633
A map of the country can be found at
<http://www.un.org/Depts/Cartographic/map/profile/iraq.pdf>. Mosul is in
the north west part of the country and Basra in the south east. Baghdad is
central. - Mod.LL]
